va%20Max|title=Gold/Platinum - Ava Max|publisher=[[Music Canada]]|accessdate=March 31, 2020}}</ref>\n* [[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]]: Platinum<ref>{{cite certification|region=New Zealand|type=single|artist=Ava Max|title=Sweet but Psycho|recent=website|id=4582|accessdate=January 18, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Syndicat national de l'\u00e9dition phonographique|SNEP]]: Platinum<ref name=\"SNEP\">{{cite web|url=https://snepmusique.com/les-certifications/?interprete=Ava%20Max|title=Ava Max: Les Certification|publisher=SNEP|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n| {{TBA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[So Am I (Ava Max song)|So Am I]]\"\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 2019\n| \u2014 || 14 || \u2014 || 58 || 21 || 2 || 23 || 16 || 18 || 13\n|\n* RIAA: Gold<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* ARIA: Platinum<ref>{{cite web |url=http://aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesSinglesAccreds2019.htm |title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations \u2013 2019 Singles |publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]] |date=August 31, 2019 |accessdate=September 9, 2019}}</ref>\n* BPI: Gold<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* BVMI: Gold<ref name=\"BVMI\"/>\n* IFPI SWI: Platinum<ref name=\"ifpi-swi\"/>\n* MC: Platinum<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n* SNEP: Gold<ref name=\"SNEP\"/>\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{n/a|Non-album singles}}<ref name=\"MTV\">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3159543/ava-max-kings-and-queens-interview/|title=Ava Max Breaks Down 'Kings & Queens,' Her Empowering Call To Arms|last=Rothman|first=Madeline|website=[[MTV News]]|date=March 12, 2020|access-date=March 12, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Torn (Ava Max song)|Torn]]\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Torn\" did not enter the [[ARIA Charts|ARIA Singles Chart]], but peaked at number 34 on the [[ARIA Digital Track Chart]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cdn.aria.com.au/pdfs/50C3CEE865E9F7C3483B1F237ACDED4FE511F1B813FAF73185BED22556B39055/ARIA%20Digital%20Tracks%20Chart.pdf?seq=26|title=ARIA Australian Top 40 Digital Tracks|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Associ